item.title: T3100e vintage computer
item.description: The Toshiba T3100e is a “luggable” PC-compatible computer introduced in 1988. It has an Intel 80286 CPU, 1 MB RAM, 20 MB hard disk, 3.5” floppy drive, and a stunning 640x400 orange monochrome gas-plasma display.
